{
  "texts": [
    "The overall ACR for the task is then calculated by aggregating the contributions of all agents for all required materials:",
    "The cooperation level can then be calculated as:",
    "Here, n is the number of agents, I ∈ R n, I i is the contribution of item agent i provides, and then we standardize the score.",
    "Farm-to-Table Cooking Dependency Complexity (D).",
    "where m i represents the direct materials required for crafting the target food item, and d i denotes the number of processing steps required to obtain or synthesize the material m i within the context of the task."
  ]
}